description:
UeMeasControl: Table containing UE measurement control parameters for various radio access technologies.

dateTime: Timestamp of the measurement control configuration.
Area_Name: Geographic area where the configuration applies (e.g., cell site location).
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
Id2:  Duplicate of CellId (redundant).
Id3: Secondary identifier potentially related to sector or equipment.
Id4:  Ancillary identifier (likely unused or placeholder).
vsDataType: Type of data record (constant value).
vsDataFormatVersion:  Version of the data format (constant value).
UeMeasControl.csfbHoTargetSearchTimer: Timer for CSFB handover target search.
UeMeasControl.bothB2RscpEcnoCheck: Boolean indicating whether to perform RSCP/ECNO check on B2 band.
UeMeasControl.a5MobilityTimerBr: Timer for A5 mobility measurement in BR mode.
UeMeasControl.measQuantityUtraFDD: Measurement quantity for UTRA FDD.
UeMeasControl.ueMeasurementsActiveIF: Boolean indicating whether UE measurements are active for inter-frequency.
UeMeasControl.filterCoefficientRscpUtra: Filter coefficient for RSCP in UTRA.
UeMeasControl.maxMeasNR: Maximum number of NR measurements.
UeMeasControl.bothIntraA3RsrpRsrqCheck: Boolean indicating whether to perform both intra-A3 RSRP/RSRQ check.
UeMeasControl.maxMeasB1Endc: Maximum number of B1 measurements in Endc.
UeMeasControl.rwrToNRAllowed: Boolean indicating whether handover from radio to NR is allowed.
UeMeasControl.nrB1MobilityTimerLessTtt: NR B1 mobility timer when TTT is less than threshold.
UeMeasControl.maxNoMeasReportsInact: Maximum number of measurement reports when inactive.
UeMeasControl.maxMeasEUtraOther: Maximum number of measurements for other EUTRA cells.
UeMeasControl.sMeasure: S-measure parameter.
UeMeasControl.endcMeasRestartTime: Time to restart Endc measurements.
UeMeasControl.filterCoefficientEUtraUlSinrMax: Filter coefficient for EUTRA UL SINR Max.
UeMeasControl.measScaleFactor: Measurement scale factor.
UeMeasControl.endcB1MeasWindow: Measurement window for Endc B1.
UeMeasControl.endcMeasTime: Measurement time for Endc.
UeMeasControl.ueMeasControlId: Unique identifier of the measurement control configuration.
UeMeasControl.ueMeasurementsActiveCDMA2000: Boolean indicating whether UE measurements are active for CDMA2000.
UeMeasControl.ulSinrOffset: Uplink SINR offset.
UeMeasControl.bothA5RsrpRsrqCheck: Boolean indicating whether to perform both A5 RSRP/RSRQ check.
UeMeasControl.maxMeasInterFreqEUtraIncR12: Maximum number of inter-frequency measurements in EUTRA including R12.
UeMeasControl.maxMeasEUtraOtherR12: Maximum number of measurements for other EUTRA cells including R12.
UeMeasControl.bothA5RsrpRsrqCheckSpifho: Boolean indicating whether to perform both A5 RSRP/RSRQ check for S-P-IFHO.
UeMeasControl.zzzTemporary18: Placeholder column (likely unused).
UeMeasControl.zzzTemporary17: Placeholder column (likely unused).
UeMeasControl.maxMeasUtraFdd: Maximum number of UTRA FDD measurements.
UeMeasControl.zzzTemporary16: Placeholder column (likely unused).
UeMeasControl.maxMeasCdma2000eHrpd: Maximum number of CDMA2000 eHRPD measurements.
UeMeasControl.prioOffsetPerQci: Priority offset per QCI.

UeMeasControl.zzzTemporary14: Placeholder column (likely unused).
UeMeasControl.zzzTemporary13: Placeholder column (likely unused).

UeMeasControl.zzzTemporary8: Placeholder column (likely unused).
UeMeasControl.excludeInterFreqAtCritical: Boolean indicating whether to exclude inter-frequency measurements at critical situations.
UeMeasControl.zzzTemporary9: Placeholder column (likely unused).
UeMeasControl.bothInterA3RsrpRsrqCheck: Boolean indicating whether to perform both inter-A3 RSRP/RSRQ check.
UeMeasControl.maxUtranCellsToMeasure: Maximum number of UTRAN cells to measure.
UeMeasControl.bothRsrpRsrqCheckUlTraffic: Boolean indicating whether to perform both RSRP/RSRQ check for uplink traffic.
UeMeasControl.targetA2UlSearchOffset: Target A2 uplink search offset.
UeMeasControl.ueMeasurementsActive: Boolean indicating whether UE measurements are active.
UeMeasControl.waitForResumeNRMeas: Time to wait for resuming NR measurements.
UeMeasControl.lowPrioMeasThresh: Threshold for low priority measurements.
UeMeasControl.maxMeasUtraTdd: Maximum number of UTRA TDD measurements.
UeMeasControl.checkA2SearchLevel: Boolean indicating whether to check A2 search level.
UeMeasControl.servOrPrioIFHoTimer: Timer for service or priority inter-frequency handover.
UeMeasControl.endcCheckForRwrToNRDisabled: Boolean indicating whether Endc check for handover to NR is disabled.
UeMeasControl.bothB1RscpEcnoCheck: Boolean indicating whether to perform RSCP/ECNO check on B1 band.
UeMeasControl.inhibitB2RsrqConfig: Boolean indicating whether to inhibit B2 RSRQ configuration.
